{"tid":224613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【共用針頭！】廣州一醫院抽血不換針頭　醫生解釋：扎兩三個而已","createTime":"2017-05-01T07:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T08:02:08.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb830a9c869a89e34abc62e076e490b2b981e9c9","tid":224613,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T07:57:11.000Z","msg":"廣東省廣州市一家醫院的醫生為病患抽血時沒有換針頭，醫生還說：「應該沒有什麼，就扎了兩三個而已」。<br />\n<br />\n陳小姐上月11日帶孩子到廣州天河區人民醫院看病，抽血檢查後，她身後的另一名患者的家人無意間聽到兩位醫生對話。女醫生大聲問男醫生：「到底有沒有換針頭？」男醫生卻說，「這個應該沒有什麼，就扎了兩三個而已」。<br />\n<br />\n目前天河區衛生和計劃生育局已經介入調查，院生說，涉事的檢查科男醫生是實習醫生，已經離職，而陳小姐發現已要求重新為孩子抽血，希望未來3年內都能追蹤體檢，並堅持要求院方合理解釋。<br />\n<br />\n（廣東電視台）<br />\n<br />\n- See more at: <a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170430/s00004/1493563271021#sthash.Cp8PocNO.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170430%2Fs00004%2F1493563271021%23sthash.Cp8PocNO.dpuf&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=f9d2b8e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170430%2Fs00004%2F1493563271021%23sthash.Cp8PocNO.dpuf&h=ea400743\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170430/s00004/1493563271021#sthash.Cp8PocNO.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"34927df97781ad7296f5ec483f17b6266e8f7f5b","tid":224613,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:02:08.000Z","msg":"對啊，老婆也是被兩三個扎而已"}]}